04dc8e48f","tid":1236480,"uid":143399,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T13:06:52.000Z","msg":"正經野要緊 醫館局 釋放義士 林鄭問責 正明遊行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"043e3b042153d1a069b611e7a80bd255cccd223b","tid":1236480,"uid":251114,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T13:06:53.000Z","msg":"可以笑 但要提醒自己唔好鬆懈 唔好變嘉年華<br />\n始終我地唔係軍人 唔係個個都可以咁嚴守軍紀 長期緊張都係一種心理壓力 間中嘅放鬆係可以 但我強調係間中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"996d87d1468944e14a1d0c2af09bff24cda032c7","tid":1236480,"uid":167186,"like":13,"dislike":0,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T13:07:13.000Z","msg":"玩唔係問題<br />\n呢個星期太沉重<br />\n冇野笑下真係會抑鬱<br />\n但笑完都要做正經野"},{"pid":"1cc88696a2787573c6e470a43aafd1d41e9f9cba","tid":1236480,"uid":25916,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"quote":{"pid":"032ac47136806defbb8c7ec6fe410df1477208cb","tid":1236480,"uid":15394,"like":3,"dislike":38,"score":-35,"quote":{"pid":"fe7fe6e6c7f073c46bae747c0c3e1d70b56f0fc2","tid":1236480,"uid":257423,"like":98,"dislike":1,"score":97,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T12:40:23.000Z","msg":"咁又唔係下下都要咁認真<br />\n打杖都要抖氣<br />\n讀書返工都要休息娛樂下<br />\n偶然有啲笑料笑下有咩唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T12:44:23.000Z","msg":"我鄧出面班勇士唔抵<br />\n我更加覺得梁生死得唔抵"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T13:08:01.000Z","msg":"唔通要24小時喊住講咩 依幾日日日都討論緊 輕鬆幾分鐘都要比你屌 再咁壓抑遲d未抗爭成功就成班放棄曬啦<br />\n人地打杖死幾千個兄弟 食飯個陣都會唱下歌仔飲下酒笑下啦on9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ae0bb9bfde7d6b00df8b689c3695f2bea8bebf45","tid":1236480,"uid":77180,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-17T13:08:01.000Z","msg":"其實無乜野<br />\n又唔係真係放低正經野唔做就去玩"},{"pid":"d1227636938f30e1d